    2026-03-17: 341.7M quota(1x), 4985 calls, CR=92.7% of visible

  Our heaviest-day multiplier:
    Pre-transition  2026-03-21: visible=356.2M, quota(1x)=359.0M → 13.1x
    Post-transition 2026-04-01: visible=374.9M, quota(1x)=377.6M → 18.9x

